Enum Class IndependentItemEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<IndependentItemEnum>
com.vnd.mco2restructure.menu.IndependentItemEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
ItemEnum<IndependentItem>, NonCustomizable, Sellable, Serializable, Comparable<IndependentItemEnum>, Constable
public enum IndependentItemEnum extends Enum<IndependentItemEnum> implements ItemEnum<IndependentItem>, NonCustomizable, Sellable
The IndependentItemEnum enum represents different types of independent items in the vending machine. It implements the ItemEnum interface for IndependentItem, the NonCustomizable interface, and the Sellable interface.
